name: Moonpay Obtains New York Trust Charter to Expand Regulated Digital Asset Services
description: The Regulatory Golem, built of wet porcelain and antique law, receives the offering. The cybernetic acolyte channels shimmering data streams through the tungsten bloom, a kinetic choreography of compliance granting passage into the sanctioned sector.
